## Supabase Database Schema

### Tables to Create

| Table | Key Columns |
|-------|-------------|
| `products` | id, title, price, original_price, category_id, badge, sizes[], colors[], description, in_stock, image_main, image_hover, images_by_color (jsonb) |
| `categories` | id, title, idx, image_url, slug |
| `orders` | id, customer_name, email, phone, address, items (jsonb), subtotal, discount, total, status, created_at |
| `customers` | id, name, email, phone, total_orders, total_spent, created_at |
| `inventory` | id, product_id, size, color, stock_qty |
| `discounts` | id, code, text, percent, active |
| `site_settings` | key, value (jsonb) — for hero slides, banners, etc. |
| `transactions` | id, order_id, amount, method, status, created_at |

### Supabase Storage Buckets
- `product-images` — product main, hover, color variant images
- `category-images` — category card images
- `hero-images` — hero carousel slides

