## Proposed Changes

### Backend — Node.js Express API

#### [NEW] `backend/package.json`
- Dependencies: express, cors, dotenv, @supabase/supabase-js, multer, uuid, jsonwebtoken

#### [NEW] `backend/index.js`
- Express server on port 3001
- CORS configured for frontend
- Routes: `/api/products`, `/api/categories`, `/api/orders`, `/api/customers`, `/api/inventory`, `/api/discounts`, `/api/auth`, `/api/settings`, `/api/transactions`

#### [NEW] `backend/routes/products.js`
- GET /api/products — list all
- GET /api/products/:id — single product
- POST /api/products — create (with image upload to Supabase Storage)
- PUT /api/products/:id — update
- DELETE /api/products/:id — delete

#### [NEW] `backend/routes/orders.js`
- GET /api/orders — list all orders (with filters: status, date)
- GET /api/orders/new — new orders for slip download
- PATCH /api/orders/:id/status — update order status
- GET /api/orders/:id/slip — generate order slip (PDF or printable HTML)

#### [NEW] `backend/routes/categories.js`, `customers.js`, `inventory.js`, `discounts.js`
- Full CRUD for each

#### [NEW] `backend/middleware/adminAuth.js`
- JWT-based admin authentication middleware

