### Admin Login Screen

#### Added inside `Admin.jsx`
- Before showing the admin panel, show a clean login screen
- Username + Password form
- Calls `POST /api/auth/admin-login` → returns JWT token
- Token stored in `sessionStorage`
- All admin API calls include `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
- "Back to store" link

